A force of nature, @LizaKoshy has rapidly made her mark as a multi-dimensional talent.

Liza’s vulnerability and willingness to share her biggest fears, has allowed her to take each video, comedy bit, and impression to the next level. Now, she’s going beyond YouTube, taking on more elevated roles. “Although I felt pressure to fill my social feed, I took the time to feed myself, my mind, and my body. I’m feeling fed, fueled and very full. And now I’m ready to #GoBeyond.”
